Salesforce (salesforce.com Germany GmbH, Erika-Mann-Strasse 31-37, 80636 Munich, Germany) supports us in processing your personal data for direct marketing purposes. If you create a customer account, subscribe to the newsletter or activate push notifications, your data will also be stored and processed in our Salesforce Cloud. In addition, Salesforce provides us with the Tableau service, which we use to analyse your data.
